# UI Component Patterns

## shadcn/ui Components

Components live in `packages/ui/src/components/` and use:
- Tailwind CSS v4 with CSS variables for theming
- `class-variance-authority` for variants
- `cn()` utility for class merging

```typescript
import { cn } from '../lib/utils';
import { cva, type VariantProps } from 'class-variance-authority';

const buttonVariants = cva(
  "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md text-sm font-medium",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "bg-primary text-primary-foreground",
        outline: "border border-input bg-background",
      },
    },
    defaultVariants: { variant: "default" },
  }
);
```

## Chat Components

- `ChatMessage` - Individual message with role-based styling
- `ChatTranscript` - Scrollable message list with auto-scroll
- `ChatInput` - Input with send button and loading state

## Timeline Components

- `TimelineEvent` - Tool execution entry with status icon
- `ThinkingTimeline` - Vertical timeline of tool executions
- `ThinkingPanel` - Collapsible reasoning display

## Export Pattern

Export all components from `src/index.ts`:

```typescript
export * from './components/button';
export * from './components/chat-message';
export { cn } from './lib/utils';
```
